<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>gẖyrt ḥyạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (gẖyrt ḥyạty bḥb ʿjyb
 wmʿạk fy smạk bqy̱ ly nṣyb)2
 1- ạkẖtrt tjyny wạ̉nạ wsṭ ạ̉nyny mdyt ly ạ̹ydyk ạlḥlwẗ wʿynyk tsbyny
 nsytny ậlạmy rjʿt slạmy wạdytny frḥẗ wbhjẗ wmsẖyt qdạmy
 2- wbḍʿfy hạjylk yạ yswʿ wạnạdylk tgẖslny bqwẗ dmk yrfʿny ṣlybk
 tsẖfy ly jrwḥy wtbdl nwḥy sʿạdẗ wnṣrẗ fy sẖkẖṣk tnʿsẖ ly rwḥy
 3- ạ̉yạmy ạljạyẗ fy ạ̹ydyk mḥmyẗ msẖ kẖạyf ʿ ạlmstqbl ʿsẖạn ạnt rạʿy
 wạṣq fy wʿwdk mlạzmny wjwdk wḥyạty ạ̹nt gẖạmrhạ bạlkẖyr mn jwdk</lyrics>
